title: The Doors - The Complete Stockholm '68 Tapes (SBD) [FLAC]
description:
The Doors - The Complete Stockholm '68 Tapes
Remastered + Pitch Corrected from Original Source (SBD Pre-FM)
Recorded live on September 20, 1968 at the Konserthuset, Stockholm, Sweden
Format: 2 x CD, Unofficial release

Unofficial Soundboard Recording - Audio Quality Very Good>Excellent

Tracklist:

Disc 1 (Early Show): 
1. Five To One
2. Love Street
3. Love Me Two Times
4. When The Music's Over
5. A Little Game
6. The Hill Dwellers
7. Light My Fire
8. The Unknown Solider

Disc 2 (Late Show):
1. Five To One
2. Mack The Knife > Alabama Song
3. Back Door Man
4. You're Lost Little Girl
5. Love Me Two Times
6. When The Music's Over
7. Wild Child
8. Money
9. Celebration of the Lizard (Wake Up!)
10. Light My Fire
11. The End


Notes: Thanks to theface07 and grner1 - you find the original info sheet in the tech folder as well as the audiochecker files I created. I only added tagging and corrected the title of track2 disc2 (Mack the Knife). maxblues
